If you're someone who comes from the left or has a left-leaning disposition, I encourage you to look at #Bitcoin not through a reflexive partisan perspective; but rather through a first-principles problem-solving perspective.

And I want to be clear, it's not about making #Bitcoin fit into a specific political narrative within the existing partisan/2-party paradigm. It's about doing the work to really examine the veracity of orthodox partisan presuppositions and the willingness to shed them.
